==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Misrepresent
<hw>Mis*rep`re*sent"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To
represent incorrectly (almost always, unfavorably); to give a false or
erroneous representation of, either maliciously, ignorantly, or
carelessly.</def> <rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misrepresent</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misrepresent
<hw>Mis*rep`re*sent"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To make an incorrect or
untrue representation.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misrepresentation</ent>⟦br⟧
